reviewText: The Movie  " Woman in the window " was Fantastic!! Well written and well acted. I like my  "old" movies in black and white but this was so good, I  forgot that it it was in color.  :)  Betrayed was as I remembered it, a well acted movie that still sickens me, especially to see in 2018 just how real racism still is.

Betrayed, One star. DVD played for 30 minutes, then stopped. Wouldn't play at all. It was not my player as I played Woman in the Window next. 5 Stars for "Woman" loved it, especially the ending, didn't pick it at all. Excellent stuff
